ch.iserver.ace.net.protocol
Interface ProtocolConstants

All Known Implementing Classes:
CollaborationParserHandler, CollaborationSerializer, ParserHandler, RequestParserHandler, ResponseParserHandler, SerializerImpl
public interface ProtocolConstants

This interface declares constants for the protocol implementation of ACE. The values of the constants directly match with the XML protocol message tags as defined in protocol.xsd.
